friends = list(map(int, input("Enter gifts: ").split()))

while friends[i] != 0:
    i += 1

    if friends[j - 1] == 0:
        friends[j - 1] = i + 1
        i += 1
    j += 1

# Print out the friends
print("Gifts: ", *friends)

def find_gifts(f):
    n = len(f)
    no_gift_to = []
    no_gift_from = []
    for i in range(n):
        if f[i] == 0:
            no_gift_to.append(i)
        else:
            if f[f[i] - 1] == 0:
                no_gift_from.append(f[i] - 1)

    # Give gifts to friends who don't know who to give gifts to
    for i in range(len(no_gift_to)):
        f[no_gift_from[i]] = no_gift_to[i] + 1

    # Give gifts to friends who don't know who gives them gifts
    for i in range(len(no_gift_to)):
        f[no_gift_to[i]] = no_gift_from[i] + 1

    return f
